*** Welcome to the Inventory Help System ***

Add Items:      Allows you to add new item.
Edit Items:     Allows you to change item already in the file.
                Prompt will appear to input item number to search for.
Remove Item:    Allows for the deletion of an item in the file that is no longer needed.
View Inventory: Allows you to view the entire inventory on screen.
Help:           Displays this information.
Exit:           Saves any unsaved datat to file and ends the program.
